description: Copy to flutter-run-params.mdc and fill with your values (do not commit secrets)
alwaysApply: true
---

# Flutter Run / Build — Required --dart-define Parameters

Copy this file to `flutter-run-params.mdc` (same folder) and replace the placeholders. **Do not commit** `flutter-run-params.mdc` if it contains real tokens.

Always append these parameters to `flutter run` and `flutter build`:

```
--dart-define=FIREBASE_API_KEY="YOUR_FIREBASE_WEB_API_KEY"
--dart-define=FIREBASE_APP_ID="YOUR_FIREBASE_APP_ID"
--dart-define=FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID="YOUR_SENDER_ID"
--dart-define=FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID="YOUR_PROJECT_ID"
--dart-define=FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET="YOUR_STORAGE_BUCKET"
--dart-define=MP_ACCESS_TOKEN_SELLER="YOUR_MERCADOPAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN"
--dart-define=MP_CREATE_PREFERENCE_HOST="YOUR_BACKEND_URL_FOR_PREFERENCES"
```

## Example

```bash
flutter run --debug \
  --dart-define=FIREBASE_API_KEY="YOUR_FIREBASE_WEB_API_KEY" \
  --dart-define=FIREBASE_APP_ID="YOUR_FIREBASE_APP_ID" \
  --dart-define=FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID="YOUR_SENDER_ID" \
  --dart-define=FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID="YOUR_PROJECT_ID" \
  --dart-define=FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET="YOUR_STORAGE_BUCKET" \
  --dart-define=MP_ACCESS_TOKEN_SELLER="YOUR_MERCADOPAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN" \
  --dart-define=MP_CREATE_PREFERENCE_HOST="YOUR_BACKEND_URL_FOR_PREFERENCES"
```
